[normal]Written Evidence from the Charity Finance Group [CEP0015][bold]&#xa0;[bold]&#xa0;[bold]Executive[bold] summary[bold]&#xa0;[bold]Charity Finance Group welcomes the opportunity to respond to this call for evidence on charity Chief Executive pay. 
[normal]CFG works with finance professionals to enable them to give the essential 
[normal]financial 
[normal]leadership that their 
[normal]charities need; it is ess
[normal]ential that charities are financially confident and trustworthy in decision making, including on pay.  We summarise our views in this submission as follows:
